examples.en: The years rolled by.
The fog soon rolled away.
Offers rolled in.
The water rolled.
The thunder rolled.
She rolled the ball
The hills rolled past.
The great river rolled on.
examples.ru: Великая река не спеша несла свои воды.

examples.en: The jet rolled into a dive.
Mist rolled in from the sea.
Tears rolled down her cheeks.
The child rolled down the hill
They rolled from town to town.
examples.ru: Они переезжали из города в город.

examples.en: The ball rolled under the car.
He rolled over on to his front.
He rolled up when it suited him.
examples.ru: Он появлялся, когда ему было удобно.

examples.en: The car rolled slowly to a stop.
The ball rolled between his feet.
The children rolled down the hill.
The car rolled over onto its side.
Pizza dough should be rolled thinly.
examples.ru: Тесто для пиццы нужно раскатывать тонко.

examples.en: He rolled the die, hoping for a six.
examples.ru: Он бросил кубик, в надежде, что выпадет шестёрка.

examples.en: The ball rolled into touch.
examples.ru: Мяч выкатился в аут /за пределы поля/.

examples.en: He rolled his shoulders back.
Thunder rolled in the distance.
The ball rolled into the street.
The ball rolled slowly to a stop.
The ball rolled underneath the car.
He finally rolled out of bed at noon.
examples.ru: В полдень он наконец-то вылез из постели.

examples.en: Nick rolled down his window and spat.
examples.ru: Ник опустил своё окошко и сплюнул.
